<https://www.gov.uk/government/people/laura-trott> <http://ogp.me/ns#description> "Laura Trott was Chief Secretary to the Treasury between 13 November 2023 and 5 July 2024. She was previously Parliamentary Under Secretary of State at the Department for Work and Pensions between 27 October 2022 and 13 November 2023."@en .
